{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"db49ba3991","title":"八项禁令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"208e099b6f","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":28,"articleId":"db49ba3991","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"77eba05c7a","name":"北京人大附中毛泽东主义红卫兵"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"755b884056","type":"title","text":"八项禁令","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36034870db","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命汹涌澎湃，一切牛鬼蛇神，剥削阶级人物胆战心惊。但是反动派是不甘心灭亡的，他们怀着刻骨的阶级仇恨，向我们最敬爱的党中央、毛主席及革命的老先辈发起了进攻。我们决不答应！决不答应！！！为防止右派翻天，特发以下禁令：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"59a0cf9724","type":"paragraph","text":"1、革命干部、军人、工农兵家里一律不得搜查，不得勒令退房、换房。已搜查过者，如没收了文件物品必须立即退回。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b75547ad2f","type":"paragraph","text":"2、军车、小队车一律不许截，更不许搜查。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af0f0e4d8c","type":"paragraph","text":"3、对党、政、军机关任何人不准随意搜查。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bc3a1d0f5","type":"paragraph","text":"4、革命干部、军人家里的保姆（非黑五类）勤务员不准勒令取消。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"602ef9d9be","type":"paragraph","text":"5、到地、富、反、坏、资产阶级家里搜查，要有本校红卫兵总部证明。没收物品一律打收条上交总部或派出所。如有趁机贪污盗窃自肥者，发现后严惩不饶。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0b4eb06c5","type":"paragraph","text":"6、黑五类子弟决不准冒充红卫兵招摇撞骗，如发现严加惩处。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f7502f173","type":"paragraph","text":"7、外地来京者因不了解本地情况，一律不准到任何地方搜查。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eab35b0281","type":"paragraph","text":"8、上公共汽车、下饭馆、买东西必须按价买，任何人不得例外（有免费证者除外）服务人员如遇上述情况应切实负起责任。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a154115c4","type":"paragraph","text":"注意事项：","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87a55df5fa","type":"paragraph","text":"l、如遇违犯上述禁令及发现各种不合理或反动传单，真正的红卫兵有全权干涉。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76a6e06086","type":"paragraph","text":"2、执行此禁令时，如遇阻力当事者可立即向人大附中毛泽东主义红卫兵报告。（电话：28局213l转596或28局1671）","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b55ec374e3","type":"paragraph","text":"只准左派造反，不准右派翻天。如要翻天，立即镇压！","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce5b8219f9","type":"paragraph","text":"真正的红卫兵立即行动起来，保卫党中央、保卫毛主席1","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76e0de897f","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政万岁！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"952b2bc688","type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的红卫兵万岁！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b8b469514","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年八日二十九日","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"db49ba3991","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}